      <title>特朗普胜选后，印度准备让卢比与人民币同步贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/india-ready-to-weaken-rupee-in-line-with-yuan-after-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据了解印度央行政策制定者想法的人士透露，在唐纳德·特朗普的选举胜利引发对美国提高关税的担忧之后，印度央行准备让卢比与人民币一起贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/india-ready-to-weaken-rupee-in-line-with-yuan-after-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Kayne Anderson 的 Rabil 谈全球投资前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-11/kayne-anderson-s-rabil-on-global-investment-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Kayne Anderson 首席执行官 Al Rabil 讨论了美国大选后他对房地产、基础设施和私人信贷等领域的展望和投资策略。他在悉尼举行的瑞银澳大利亚年度会议间隙就“彭博：亚洲贸易”接受了 Haidi Stroud-Watts 的独家采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-11/kayne-anderson-s-rabil-on-global-investment-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 01:08:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
